I just saw the NBC made-for-TV movie about the events that led up to the raid<br>
on the Mt. Carmel complex.  The Seventh-day Adventist church was never <br>
mentioned by name, and oblique references were few.  The details seem <br>
to match most of the other things we have heard.  Lots of shooting, lots<br>
of preaching before the shooting. <br>
<p>
Has anyone figured out who this John Ellis character is yet?  Those<br>
advertisements of the "Worldwide Council of SDA" are nothing but trouble.<br>
<p>
Steve Timm<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
