Bruce writes:<br>
<p>
	Yes, the Bible says "Thou shalt not kill" but I think . . .<br>
<p>
<p>
	As head of our household, I don't think . . .`<br>
<p>
I'm fascinated by the selective interpretation of "Thus saith the Holy One."<br>
<p>
Bruce continues:<br>
<p>
	What do you all think?  I would appreciate Bible texts . . .<br>
<p>
I think that we will give the interpretation to Bible texts that reinforce our previously formed opinions.  We will search to find texts that make us <br>
look good in the positions we have chosen to assume in life.  We will attempt<br>
to use the Holy One to strengthen our humanly defined position even if it<br>
means that we are subjugating another human being.<br>
<p>
Sue Harrington<br>
