The basis of American culture, and success is the concept of the free man,<br>
with land.  Our founding fathers adopted the philosphy that the only way to<br>
be truely free, is to be able to hold (own) land, and the means to defend it.<br>
Guns have been traditionaly, the weapons of choice.  An armed, freeman is the<br>
best insurance against tyranny.  Thus gun ownership is critical to making the<br>
US what it is. <br>
Cheers<br>
Woody<br>
