<title>May_1993: Re: Guns, Guns</title>
<h1>Re: Guns, Guns</h1>
Steve Hix (<i>fiddler@dobbs.eng.sun.com</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 25 May 93 12:24:03 PDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#261">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#261">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#261">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#261">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0262.html">Harvey Brenneise: "Re: Censored Newsgroups @ WWC (fwd)"</a>
