<title>May_1993: Re: Guns, Guns</title>
<h1>Re: Guns, Guns</h1>
Marcus Stringer (<i>marcuss@microsoft.com</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 26 May 93 09:17:43 PDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#277">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#277">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#277">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#277">[ author ]</a>
