Dear SDAnetters,<br>
<p>
In the past few weeks there have been a lot of posts on Koresh, guns and<br>
homosexuality.  While these are important topics, they're also getting<br>
to be a little on the heavy side.<br>
<p>
So, in the spirit of Ecclesiastes ("There is a time to weep and a time<br>
to laugh...."), I'm asking if anyone out there knows of any BBS's<br>
devoted to animation.  Lists for fans of Japanese animation ("anime")<br>
would be especially appreciated.  I have an address for fans of "The<br>
Simpsons" but am also looking for something a little more broad<br>
spectrum.  Thanks in advance.<br>
<p>
Daniel J. Drazen<br>
Editor, SDA Periodical Index<br>
