Steve,<br>
<p>
I don't personally know of any bad press on my neighbors the Moores.<br>
<p>
But I was within ear shot when he was explaining how things ran awry<br>
with a non-SDA employee who basically took over the way his institute<br>
was being run.  Moore's ended up having to leave the organization<br>
they founded in our little town of Washougal.  I don't have the details<br>
on his new organization or if its even a formalized enterprize.  But<br>
hey, I could call and find out the latest on what he is up to.<br>
<p>
DaveB<br>
