<title>Apr_1992: Re: Let me see if I have this correct</title>
<h1>Re: Let me see if I have this correct</h1>
Scott Mattes (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Mon, 20 Apr 1992 10:29:30 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#40">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#40">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#40">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#40">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
