<title>Apr_1992: Re: After Death - Soul/Spirit</title>
<h1>Re: After Death - Soul/Spirit</h1>
Scott Mattes (<i>COTRSSM@sea04vm.navsea.navy.mil</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 21 Apr 92 11:18:34 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#55">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#55">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#55">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#55">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0056.html">Bill Oblitey: "Re: Let me see if I have this correct on saved by works"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0054.html">Eric Snyder: "Death/Afterlife"</a>
