<title>Apr_1992: Did Jesus talk 'strangely'?</title>
<h1>Did Jesus talk 'strangely'?</h1>
Scott Mattes (<i>COTRSSM@sea04vm.navsea.navy.mil</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 24 Apr 92 11:20:51 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#82">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#82">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#82">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#82">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0083.html">David Plaisted: "Soul sleep"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0081.html">Eric Snyder: "The Trinity"</a>
