[Scott writes]<br>
<i>&gt;  What does your church say is the fate awaiting all those who died not</i><br>
<i>&gt;knowing of the need for baptism or even that Jesus lived and died for</i><br>
<i>&gt;thier sins?</i><br>
<p>
Romans chapter 2 is a good one to read on this topic.<br>
<p>
Those who respond to Jesus, through the Holy Spirit working upon their<br>
conscience are more savable than those who merely say "Lord Lord",<br>
knowing Jesus, but without the power in evidence.<br>
<p>
DaveB<br>
