<title>Apr_1992: Re: After Death - Soul/Spirit</title>
<h1>Re: After Death - Soul/Spirit</h1>
Dave Buxton (<i>davidbu@loowit.wr.tek.com</i>)<br>
<i>Mon, 27 Apr 92 11:20:34 PDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#91">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#91">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#91">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#91">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0092.html">Eric Snyder: "Death/Afterlife"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0090.html">Nancy Vyhmeister: "Re: Perseverance"</a>
<li> <b>Maybe in reply to:</b> <a href="0028.html">Eric Snyder: "After Death - Soul/Spirit"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
