The etexts are on<br>
mrcnext:  cd etext/etext91, 92, 93,<br>
quake.think.com:  cd pub then cd etext91, 92, 93<br>
simtel20.army.mil:  cd pd1:&lt;msdos.books&gt;<br>
nptn.org:  cd /pub/e.texts/gutenberg then cd etext91, 92, 93<br>
