<!-- body="start" -->
Hello Steve,<br>
    I too am impressed on how well everyone on the net has done in<br>
presenting a well-balanced view of Adventism on the Christia net.<br>
Wouldn't it be a good idea for one or more of the major participants<br>
to write something up for inclusion in the Adventist Review?  I am<br>
sure a lot of Adventists would be very interested in how the Branch<br>
Davidian issue has provided opportunities for electronic witnessing.<br>
<p>
    This network is one of the few places I have found where<br>
Adventists from the entire theological spectrum within the Adventist<br>
church can be free to state what they believe without fear of being<br>
"flamed".  I truly believe our churches would be a lot more attractive<br>
places if we all spent more time trying to understand each other<br>
rather than in judgement and condemning each other.  Keep up the good<br>
work everyone!<br>
<p>
<pre>
-- 
Gary W. Burdick (burdick@hkuxa.hku.hk)
Department of Physics, University of Hong Kong, Pokfulam Rd, HONG KONG
</pre>
