To Bruce and Ruben...<br>
<p>
There are many tangents in which we could direct our energies.<br>
Fortunately, I've not followed this one.  But I like this statement from Bruce:<br>
<p>
<i>	&gt;How about spending your bandwidth time building up people's faith</i><br>
<i>	&gt;in the Word of God instead of trying to tear it down.</i><br>
<p>
Don't take it personal Ruben.  We all (myself being chief) need to spend more<br>
time building our faith in the Word of God.  But I'll go even farther<br>
than Bruce,<br>
to say that there is a greater need for us to hunger and thirst after<br>
the Word Who<br>
&lt;IS&gt; God (John 1:1,2), which the Bible serves only as a map.<br>
<p>
Marcus S at Microsoft<br>
