Ruben Gonzalez:<br>
Of course now its over to all of you to show me how wrong I am. :^)<br>
<p>
Marcus Stringer:<br>
No Ruben, you are right in more ways than you think!<br>
This is why I love the discussions about the AntiChrist.  It makes us<br>
go back to our first love.  Not the laws of Moses, not even the Sabbath.<br>
In order to appreciate the "real thing", we have to keep our eyes fixed<br>
on Jesus THE Christ, or we all are antiCHRIST-like - - setting ourselves<br>
and traditions up in the place of Christ.<br>
<p>
Thanks Ruben.<br>
