<title>Apr_1993: SDAnet - RE:  Maxwell's letter</title>
<h1>SDAnet - RE:  Maxwell's letter</h1>
Marcus Stringer (<i>marcuss@microsoft.com</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 30 Mar 93 09:54:22 PST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#31">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#31">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#31">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#31">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
