<title>Apr_1993: Re: SDA: America</title>
<h1>Re: SDA: America</h1>
Noe Torres | ECISD (<i>noe@tenet.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 2 Apr 1993 08:39:57 -0600 (CST)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#106">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#106">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#106">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#106">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0107.html">Noe Torres | ECISD: "The Generation That Forgot God."</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0105.html">Noe Torres | ECISD: "Strange imagery."</a>
