<title>Apr_1993: The Generation That Forgot God.</title>
<h1>The Generation That Forgot God.</h1>
Noe Torres | ECISD (<i>noe@tenet.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 2 Apr 1993 10:19:30 -0600 (CST)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#107">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#107">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#107">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#107">[ author ]</a>
