<h1>Re: Long-term visitors</h1>
darrell tinker (<i>darrellt@ross.com</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 2 Apr 93 17:54:23 CST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#97">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#97">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#97">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#97">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0098.html">Gregg Wisdom: "end times"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0096.html">Vice-Dean Jerry Wiley - x06473: "Reply to Bill Allen"</a>
