To Beng:<br>
<p>
Beng, I guess it depends a lot on a person's definition of an evangelical. <br>
I subscribe to the fact that Adventist's are evangelicals. The reason I <br>
believe we are is due to the fact that evangelicals  are protestants who <br>
emphasize salvation by faith in the atonement of Jesus, and reject the <br>
efficacy of the sacraments and good works alone.<br>
