<title>Apr_1993: Re: The real issues? (Dr. Ralph Larson)</title>
<h1>Re: The real issues? (Dr. Ralph Larson)</h1>
Noe Torres | ECISD (<i>noe@tenet.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Mon, 5 Apr 1993 08:31:28 -0500 (CDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#136">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#136">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#136">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#136">[ author ]</a>
