I don't know the legal details of Ademir's friend, so would first advise<br>
her not to break any details of the divorce settlement or custody rulings.<br>
It seems that the key thing which will need to be put into the life of <br>
this nine-year old girl is a positive involvement with religious things.<br>
Most Primary Sabbath Schools, alas, are not well-equipped in this regard.<br>
If they move to Elmhurst, IL, the girl can be in our puppet troupe.<br>
But perhaps there is some other challenge.  My folks promised me a stereo<br>
system at about that age if I learned a substancial list of memory verses.<br>
<p>
The other alternative is just to experiment with letting the girl have<br>
some of what she wants and discover the emptiness of things.  It's not <br>
clear that at nine years old she would be mature enough to learn that lesson.<br>
