It should be remembered that Christ comes for each person in his/her lifetime.<br>
Effectivly, when one dies, Christ comes for them, because the next thing they<br>
will know is Christs coming.  From that point of view, with life being so fragile<br>
it makes total sense to belive that Christs coming is immenent, and to prepare<br>
for it.  It could happen any time to you.<br>
Cheers<br>
Woody<br>
