<!-- body="start" -->
The best biblical support for a relation with Christ comes from texts such as<br>
John 15.  "Abiding" in Christ means a close union, a relation.  You might <br>
also look at the "in Christ" passages of Paul.<br>
<p>
This is perhaps a different way of speaking than we use now, but the meaning<br>
is quite the same, I think.<br>
<p>
Nancy<br>
