<h1>Re: The real issues</h1>
Fred Christiansen (<i>fredch@quad4.phx.mcd.mot.com</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 6 Apr 93 11:41:53 MST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#162">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#162">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#162">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#162">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0163.html">Fred Christiansen: "Re: Dillema... What to do in this situation!"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0161.html">Ruben Gonzalez: "Re: The real issues? (Dr. Ralph Larson)"</a>
