Well let me start that I really don't know R.Larson too well.<br>
<p>
I have read two of his books ("Tell of His Power" and "The Word was Made Flesh"<br>
and the Issues pamphlet he wrote. I must agree with him with regard to his <br>
position regarding the fact that the SDA doctrines have been changed/ were <br>
changed in 1952 with the Walter Martin Saga.<br>
<p>
