<p>
<i>&gt; his methods of being openly critical and denunciatory toward the</i><br>
<i>&gt; denomination?</i><br>
<p>
Since as I said I don't know him very well niether am I exposed to<br>
what the situations are over in the US in which he is involved. So I can't <br>
really comment further. I have no first hand knowledge about what he is <br>
involved in. <br>
<p>
As far as the concept of a remnant within the SDA church, which is a major<br>
critism of all the independant ministries. All I can say is that there only<br>
ever was a remnant of Israel that was saved. and Paul tells us that that<br>
was an example for us who live in the last days. Obviously no all SDAs will<br>
be saved just like all evangelicals will not be saved.<br>
<p>
