<title>Apr_1993: Re:  The Sovereignty of God</title>
<h1>Re:  The Sovereignty of God</h1>
TANG BENG YONG (<i>med10014@nusunix2.nus.sg</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 6 Apr 93 12:50:58 +0800</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#141">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#141">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#141">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#141">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0142.html">Ruben Gonzalez: "Re: SDA: advent"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0140.html">Ademir P. Soares: "Dillema... What to do in this situation!"</a>
