Dear Steve,<br>
<p>
This is one of the basics of so-called "reformed" theology.  Many<br>
evangelicals seem to believ as one poster said that SAtan is the ruler<br>
of this earth.  However, as part of the Great Commision speach given by<br>
Christ prior to HIs ascension, He said that all authourity on earth has<br>
been given unto Him.  Later in Romans, Paul ackowledges that not all<br>
things appear to be under the authourity of Christ, but they still are.  <br>
<p>
Christ is King of kings and Lord of lords.  If you want to send me your<br>
snail mail address, I can send you a copy of a pamphlet put out by the<br>
RPCNA that deals with the issue of how Christ is King.<br>
<p>
Ray the kop<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
