<title>Apr_1993: Re: Relationship theology</title>
<h1>Re: Relationship theology</h1>
Marcus Stringer (<i>marcuss@microsoft.com</i>)<br>
<i>Wed,  7 Apr 93 09:56:58 PDT</i>
