<title>Apr_1993: Re: What I think everyone agrees on</title>
<h1>Re: What I think everyone agrees on</h1>
Sherman Cox (<i>scox@uahcs2.cs.uah.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 7 Apr 93 15:35:07 CDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#166">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#166">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#166">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#166">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
