<title>Apr_1993: Iniquities and separation from God</title>
<h1>Iniquities and separation from God</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Wed,  7 Apr 1993 22:32:01 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#188">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#188">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#188">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#188">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0189.html">PHTH1@cc.newcastle.edu.au: "I'm sorry..."</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0187.html">Fred Christiansen: "Re: What I think everyone agrees on"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
