<h1>Original sin</h1>
<i>PHTH1@cc.newcastle.edu.au</i><br>
<i>08 Apr 1993 08:39:28 +1000</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#177">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#177">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#177">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#177">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0178.html">Steven Timm: "Re: What I think everyone agrees on"</a>
