I apologize for using the term CB in this discussion...I didn't realize<br>
so many messages would be required to sort out what CB means!<br>
<p>
For those of you who wish to know what I meant when I said CB in my<br>
original question, refer to *my* definition of "CB". For those wishing<br>
to know how the term originated, and what it really *should* refer to<br>
(as opposed to what it often does), read Ruben's definition! I don't<br>
think I'll use the term again myself, it seems prone to be misunderstood<br>
in one way or another!<br>
