<h1>Humanity of Christ</h1>
David Plaisted (<i>plaisted@cs.unc.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 9 Apr 93 15:36:41 -0400</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#205">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#205">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#205">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#205">[ author ]</a>
