<!-- nextthread="start" -->
</ul>
<!-- body="start" -->
How do you know all those things about Adam &amp; Eve? Where you there? &lt;&lt;Just <br>
kidding!&gt;&gt;I am sticking with the theory and it is just not a theory -- that <br>
Eve wandered away from Adam!<br>
<p>
Cheers and all that kind of stuff! Have a Happy Easter Sunday!<br>
