<i>&gt; I am looking for a English Bibel for PC (MS DOS) with concordance.</i><br>
<i>&gt; Can someone give me a ftp-address where I can get this software.</i><br>
<p>
I know of three types of sources for this.<br>
<p>
1.  The current issue of Christianity Today has an insert with a table<br>
that reviews about 25 PC Bible packages.  Some of these are quite<br>
inexpensive.<br>
<p>
2.  You can get CD-ROMs with something like 9 versions plus<br>
concordances on them.<br>
<p>
3.  You can get the KJV raw text via FTP as described below.  You can<br>
also get all kinds of other texts such as the CIA World Factbook.<br>
<p>
Glen McCluskey<br>
glenm@usl.com<br>
