<h1>Re: Spiritual head of the family</h1>
Marcus Stringer (<i>marcuss@microsoft.com</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 15 Apr 93 19:48:51 PDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#293">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#293">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#293">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#293">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0294.html">Scott  Bechtel: "Union"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0292.html">Steve Hix: "Re: The last gap"</a>
