<!-- body="start" -->
<i>&gt; What is the Project Gutenberg Newsletter?</i><br>
<p>
Project Gutenberg's purpose in life is to make electronic versions of<br>
book texts available.  They so far have about 50 of these.<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
