Ademir P. Soares                National Aeronatics Space Administration<br>
Supv of Dataprocessing          Goddard Institute for Space Studies<br>
OPAPS@NASAGISS.GOV.NASA.GOV     2880 Broadway Ave. Roon 230<br>
                                New York, NY 10025<br>
