OK, it seems like I need to rephrase part of my original post, where I <br>
asked for people's summaries of how they think an SDA should differ from,<br>
say, a Seventh-day Baptist.<br>
<p>
I said something like "Don't get me wrong, I am the last person to say<br>
we should dwell on our distinctives."<br>
<p>
