<title>Apr_1993: Background on Ruben's post</title>
<h1>Background on Ruben's post</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 20 Apr 1993 00:50:00 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#316">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#316">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#316">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#316">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0317.html">McCluskey G: "iron"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0315.html">Ruben Gonzalez: "Sin, Christ and Salvation"</a>
